    • fillDB

      public void fillDB(String fn)
      Fills the database with data from a txt file. The file should contain information in a specific format. The expected file format: Number of authors: X Author: 1; Name: John Doe; birthDate: 1980-12-15; Address: 123 Main St; Affiliation: University; penName: J.D.; ORCID: 0000-0001-2345-6789; scienceID: 123456; googleScholarID: ABCD1234; ScopusAuthorID: 56789 Paper: reeeeeg1; Title: A horta ;Keywords: null ; anAbstract: null ; Date: 11/15/2020 ; TotalNumViews: 50000 ; TotalNumLikes: 50000 ; numDownloads: 9873100; editionNumber: 2 ; Local: Porto Author: 2; Name: Jane Smith; birthDate: 1975-11-20; Address: 456 Elm St; Affiliation: Institute; penName: J.S.; ORCID: 0000-0002-3456-7890; scienceID: 789012; googleScholarID: EFGH5678; ScopusAuthorID: 12345

      public void saveDBTxt(String fn)
